           TOTEM-IDX1), 
                       ", FILE STATUS ", PRIMARY-ERROR "," 
                       SECONDARY-ERROR
                    DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO TOTEM-MSG-2
                    MOVE SPACES TO TOTEM-MSG-3
                    MOVE MB-ERROR-ICON TO TOTEM-MSG-ICON-TYPE
                    MOVE MB-OK TO TOTEM-MSG-BUTTON-TYPE
